// Custom debounce function to replace lodash.debounce
const debounce = (func, delay) => {
 let timeoutId;
 return (...args) => {
 clearTimeout(timeoutId);
 timeoutId = setTimeout(() => func.apply(null, args), delay);
 };
};

 async callScriptInclude(methodName, parameters = {}) {

 try {
 console.log('Creating GlideAjax for method:', methodName);
 console.log('Parameters:', parameters);
 
 const ga = new GlideAjax(this.scriptInclude);
 ga.addParam('sysparm_name', methodName);
 
 // Add all parameters
 Object.keys(parameters).forEach(key => {
 ga.addParam('sysparm_' + key, parameters[key]);
 });

 ga.getXMLAnswer((response) => {
 try {
 console.log('Raw server response:', response);
 
 if (!response) {
 reject(new Error('Empty response from server'));
 return;
 }

 const result = JSON.parse(response);
 console.log('Parsed analysis result:', result);
 resolve(result);
 } catch (parseError) {
 console.error('Parse error:', parseError, 'Response:', response);
 reject(new Error('Failed to parse server response: ' + parseError.message));
 }
 });
 } catch (error) {

 reject(new Error('Failed to setup server request: ' + error.message));
 }

 }

 const type = event.type;
 let title, subtitle, duration, description, achievements, icon;

 if (type === 'field_change') {
 title = event.change_description;
 subtitle = event.user;
 duration = new Date(event.timestamp).toLocaleDateString();
 description = type.replace('_', ' ').toUpperCase();
 achievements = [];
 icon = getEventIcon(event);
 } else {
 // Comment or work note
 title = type === 'comment' ? 'Comment Added' : 'Work Note Added';
 subtitle = event.user;
 duration = new Date(event.timestamp).toLocaleDateString();
 description = event.content.length > 150
 ? event.content.substring(0, 150) + '...'
 : event.content;
 achievements = event.content.length > 150 ? [event.content.substring(150)] : [];
 icon = type === 'comment' ? ']]><![CDATA[' : ']]><![CDATA[';
 }

 return {
 id: index,
 type: type,
 title: title,
 subtitle: subtitle,
 duration: duration,
 description: description,
 achievements: achievements,
 icon: icon,
 timestamp: event.timestamp
 };
 });

 const toggleExpand = (id) => {
 setExpandedId(expandedId === id ? null : id);
 };

 if (timelineItems.length === 0) {
 return <div className="no-timeline-data">No timeline events available</div>;
 }

 return (
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-container">
 {/* Scrollable timeline viewport */}
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-viewport">
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-events-container">
 {timelineItems.map((item) => (
 <div key={item.id} className="horizontal-timeline-item">
 {/* Timeline point */}
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-point">
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-dot">
 <span className="horizontal-timeline-icon">{item.icon}</span>
 </div>
 </div>

 {/* Event card */}
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-card">
 <div
 className="horizontal-event-card"
 onClick={() => toggleExpand(item.id)}
 >
 <div className="horizontal-event-header">
 <span className="horizontal-event-icon">{item.icon}</span>
 <h3 className="horizontal-event-title">{item.title}</h3>
 </div>
 <p className="horizontal-event-subtitle">{item.subtitle}</p>
 <p className="horizontal-event-duration">{item.duration}</p>
 <p className="horizontal-event-description">{item.description}</p>

 {/* Expandable achievements */}
 <div
 className="horizontal-event-achievements"
 style={{
 maxHeight: expandedId === item.id ? '500px' : '0',
 opacity: expandedId === item.id ? 1 : 0,
 transition: 'all 0.3s ease'
 }}
 >
 {item.achievements && item.achievements.length > 0 && (
 <div className="horizontal-achievements-list">
 <h4 className="horizontal-achievements-title">Full Content:</h4>
 {item.achievements.map((achievement, i) => (
 <p key={i} className="horizontal-achievement-item">{achievement}</p>
 ))}
 </div>
 )}
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 ))}
 </div>
 </div>

 {/* Timeline bar connector */}
 <div className="horizontal-timeline-bar"></div>
 </div>
 );
}

// Timeline Event Component
function TimelineEvent({ event, isLast }) {
 const getEventIcon = (event) => {
 switch (event.type) {
 case 'field_change':
 if (event.field === 'state') return ']]><![CDATA[';
 if (event.field === 'priority') return '';
 if (event.field === 'assigned_to' || event.field === 'assignment_group') return ']]><![CDATA[';
 return '';
 case 'comment':
 return ']]><![CDATA[';
 case 'work_note':
 return ']]><![CDATA[';
 default:
 return ']]><![CDATA[';
 }
 };

 const getEventColor = (event) => {
 switch (event.type) {
 case 'field_change': return '#0073e6';
 case 'comment': return '#28a745';
 case 'work_note': return '#ffc107';
 default: return '#6c757d';
 }
 };

 return (
 <div className="timeline-item">
 {!isLast && <div className="timeline-line"></div>}

 <div className="timeline-node">
 <div
 className="timeline-dot"
 style={{ backgroundColor: getEventColor(event) }}
 >
 <span className="timeline-icon">{getEventIcon(event)}</span>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div className="timeline-content">
 <div className="timeline-header">
 <span className="timeline-user">{event.user}</span>
 <span className="timeline-time">
 {new Date(event.timestamp).toLocaleDateString()} {new Date(event.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' })}
 </span>
 </div>

 <div className="timeline-body">
 {event.type === 'field_change' ? (
 <div className="timeline-change">
 <span className="change-text">{event.change_description}</span>
 <span className="event-type-badge">{event.type.replace('_', ' ')}</span>
 </div>
 ) : (
 <div className="timeline-note">
 <div className="note-header">
 <span className="note-type">{event.type === 'comment' ? ']]><![CDATA[ Comment' : ']]><![CDATA[ Work Note'}</span>
 </div>
 <div className="note-content">
 {event.content.length > 200 ?
 event.content.substring(0, 200) + '...' :
 event.content
 }
 </div>
 </div>
 )}
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 );
}

// Metric Item Component
function MetricItem({ icon, label, value, subtitle, status }) {
 return (
 <div className="metric-item">
 <div className="metric-header">
 <span className="metric-icon">{icon}</span>
 <span className="metric-label">{label}</span>
 </div>
 <div className="metric-value">{value}</div>
 {subtitle && <div className="metric-subtitle">{subtitle}</div>}
 {status && <div className={`metric-status ${status}`}>{status}</div>}
 </div>
 );
}

 border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 115, 230, 0.15);
}

.horizontal-event-icon {
 font-size: 1.3rem;
 opacity: 0.9;
}

.horizontal-event-title {
 font-size: 1.05rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 color: #1a202c;
 margin: 0;
 flex: 1;
 line-height: 1.3;
}

.horizontal-event-subtitle {
 font-size: 0.85rem;
 font-weight: 600;
 color: #64748b;
 margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
}

.horizontal-event-subtitle:before {
 content: '';
 margin-right: 0.25rem;
 font-size: 0.7rem;
 opacity: 0.8;
}

.horizontal-event-duration {
 font-size: 0.75rem;
 color: #a0aec0;
 margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
 font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Inconsolata', 'Fira Code', monospace;
 background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.8);
 padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
 border-radius: 8px;
 display: inline-block;
 border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.3);
}

.horizontal-event-description {
 font-size: 0.9rem;
 color: #4a5568;
 line-height: 1.5;
 margin-bottom: 1rem;
 overflow-wrap: break-word;
}

.horizontal-event-achievements {
 overflow: hidden;
 transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.horizontal-achievements-list {
 padding-top: 1rem;
 border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 115, 230, 0.15);
}

.horizontal-achievements-title {
 font-size: 0.8rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 color: #0073e6;
 margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.horizontal-achievement-item {
 font-size: 0.85rem;
 color: #374151;
 line-height: 1.6;

 border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.6);
 overflow-wrap: break-word;
}

.horizontal-achievement-item:last-child {
 border-bottom: none;
}

/* Timeline bar connector */
.horizontal-timeline-bar {
 position: absolute;
 bottom: 0;
 left: 75px;
 right: 75px;
 height: 4px;
 background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0073e6 0%, rgba(0, 115, 230, 0.3) 100%);
 border-radius: 3px;
 box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 115, 230, 0.25);
 z-index: 1;
}

/* Responsive horizontal timeline */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
 .horizontal-timeline-events-container {
 gap: 0;
 padding: 0 1rem 2rem 1rem;
 }

 .horizontal-timeline-item {
 width: 280px;
 }

 .horizontal-timeline-card {
 width: 240px;
 }

 .horizontal-timeline-dot {
 width: 45px;
 height: 45px;
 }

 .horizontal-timeline-bar {
 left: 68px;
 right: 68px;
 }
}

/* No data state for horizontal timeline */
.no-timeline-data {
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
 justify-content: center;
 min-height: 250px;
 color: #a0aec0;
 font-style: italic;
 font-size: 0.95rem;
 background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.6);
 border-radius: 12px;
 border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.4);
 backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}

/* Debrief Section */
.debrief-section {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 1.5rem;
}

/* Overview */
.overview-grid {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 1.5rem;
}

.overview-item {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 0.5rem;
}

.overview-label {
 font-size: 0.8rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 color: #718096;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.overview-value {
 font-size: 0.95rem;
 color: #4a5568;
 line-height: 1.7;
 margin: 0;
 background: #f8fafc !important;
 padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
 border-radius: 10px;
 border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}

/* Actions Card */
.actions-grid {
 display: grid;
 grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));

}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
 .actions-grid {
 grid-template-columns: 1fr;
 }
}

.action-section {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 1rem;
}

.section-title {
 font-size: 1.05rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 color: #2d3748;
 margin: 0;
 padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
 border-bottom: 2px solid #0073e6;
 display: inline-block;
}

.action-list {
 list-style: none;
 padding: 0;
 margin: 0;
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 0.85rem;
}

.action-item {
 background: #f8fafc !important;
 padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
 border-radius: 10px;
 border-left: 3px solid #0073e6;
 font-size: 0.9rem;
 line-height: 1.6;
 color: #4a5568;
}

.no-data {
 background: #f8fafc !important;
 padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
 text-align: center;
 color: #a0aec0;
 font-style: italic;
 border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Metrics Row */
.metrics-grid {
 display: flex;
 flex-wrap: wrap;
 gap: 1.25rem;
}

.metric-item {
 background: #f8fafc !important;
 padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
 border-radius: 12px;
 border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
 text-align: center;
}

.metric-header {
 display: flex;
 align-items: center;
 justify-content: center;
 gap: 0.6rem;
 margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.metric-icon {
 font-size: 1.4rem;
}

.metric-label {
 font-size: 0.8rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 color: #718096;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.metric-value {
 font-size: 1.8rem;
 font-weight: 800;
 color: #0073e6;
 margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.metric-subtitle {
 font-size: 0.85rem;
 color: #a0aec0;
}

.metric-status {
 padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
 border-radius: 999px;
 font-size: 0.75rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 letter-spacing: 0.5px;
 margin-top: 0.75rem;
}

.metric-status.resolved {
 background: #e8f5e9;
 color: #2e7d32;
 border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
}

.metric-status.active {
 background: #fff8e1;
 color: #f9a825;
 border: 1px solid #ffecb3;
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 1200px) {
 .content-grid {
 grid-template-columns: 1fr;
 gap: 2rem;
 }

 .timeline-container {
 max-height: 55vh;
 }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
 .analysis-page {
 padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
 gap: 2rem;
 }

 .analysis-back-button {
 margin: 0 1rem;
 padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
 font-size: 0.9rem;
 }

 .header-card {
 padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
 margin: -2.75rem -1.5rem 2rem -1.5rem;
 }

 .incident-number {
 font-size: 2.2rem;
 }

 .incident-status-grid {

 }

 .card-header {
 padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
 flex-direction: column;
 align-items: flex-start;
 gap: 0.5rem;
 }

 .card-content {
 padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
 }

 .timeline-container {
 padding: 1rem;

 }

 .timeline-item {
 gap: 1rem;
 }

 .timeline-dot {

 height: 36px;
 }

 .timeline-content {
 padding: 1.25rem;
 }

 .metrics-grid {
 grid-template-columns: 1fr;
 }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
 .analysis-page {
 padding: 1rem 0.75rem;
 }

 .header-card {
 padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
 }

 .incident-number {
 font-size: 2rem;

 .incident-description {

 padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
 }

 .overview-value,
 .action-item {
 font-size: 0.88rem;
 }

 .metric-value {
 font-size: 1.6rem;
 }
}

export default function App() {

 const [incidentSysId, setIncidentSysId] = useState(null);

 useEffect(() => {
 // Parse URL parameters
 const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
 const sysId = urlParams.get('sys_id');
 
 if (sysId) {
 setIncidentSysId(sysId);
 setCurrentPage('analysis');
 } else {
 setCurrentPage('landing');
 }

 // Set up global navigate function as requested
 window.navigate = {
 to: (page, params = {}) => {
 if (page === 'analysis' && params.sys_id) {
 setIncidentSysId(params.sys_id);
 setCurrentPage('analysis');
 
 // Update URL without page reload
 const newUrl = new URL(window.location);
 newUrl.searchParams.set('sys_id', params.sys_id);
 window.history.pushState({}, '', newUrl);
 } else if (page === 'landing') {
 setCurrentPage('landing');
 setIncidentSysId(null);
 
 // Update URL without page reload
 const newUrl = new URL(window.location);
 newUrl.searchParams.delete('sys_id');
 window.history.pushState({}, '', newUrl);
 }
 }
 };

 // Cleanup function to remove global navigate
 return () => {
 delete window.navigate;
 };
 }, []);

 const navigateToAnalysis = (sysId) => {
 window.navigate.to('analysis', { sys_id: sysId });
 };

 const navigateToLanding = () => {
 window.navigate.to('landing');
 };

 return (
 <div className="app">
 <main className="app-main">
 {currentPage === 'landing' ? (
 <LandingPage onNavigateToAnalysis={navigateToAnalysis} />
 ) : (
 <AnalysisPage
 incidentSysId={incidentSysId}
 onNavigateToLanding={navigateToLanding}
 />
 )}
 </main>
 </div>
 );
}
